      • ExperimentCommand

        public ExperimentCommand​(long time,
                         java.lang.String client,
                         java.lang.String command)
        Constructs an experiment command object given the timestamp, client name, and command string.
        Parameters:
        time - The timestamp (in seconds) for which to execute this command.
        client - A string uniquely identifying the client to send this command to ('all' will send it to every client)
        command - The command to send to the client.
